-- VTB Hires St. Petersburg Official Molchanov, Kommersant Says
-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 2012-02-21T04:56:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-21/vtb-hires-st-petersburg-official-molchanov-kommersant-says.html
VTB Group (VTBR)  hired St. Petersburg’s
former vice-governor, Yuri Molchanov, to supervise the bank’s
infrastructure projects,  Kommersant  said, citing the bank’s
press service.  Molchanov, who worked with his then colleague and now Prime
Minister  Vladimir Putin  at Leningrad State University in
developing the university’s international ties, was appointed
VTB’s senior vice president as of Feb. 14, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story: Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow
   msysoyeva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story: Claudia
Carpenter at   ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  